m\": \"the stintMatt Hudson-Smithspent\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world's fastest man was perpetually perplexed by the British 400metre runner's penchant for never drying his feet after a shower, how fine he cut it time wise to make practice and his generally carefree attitude.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9190450049990107, \"rank\": 0.08497687590959202, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world's fastest man\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"his feet\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"a shower\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"his generally carefree attitude\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Lyles is also adamant Hudson-Smith is so good he will end up being knighted by the king one day.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9409274288979625, \"rank\": 0.06276087876145789, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the king\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair seem like perhaps unlikely former housemates but, come Wednesday, Hudson-Smith is aiming to emulateLyles as an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"perhaps unlikely former housemates\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"emulateLyles\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Lyles is focused on repeating the sprint treble he achieved at last year's World Athletics Championships in Budapest, Hudson-Smith is adamant his occasional training partner is no sort of inspiration.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9997860894624495, \"rank\": 0.00015972704650357939, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.998352841918192, \"rank\": 0.0016498756872134735, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"his occasional training partner\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"no sort\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His success does not actually inspire me in the slightest as I inspire myself,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His success\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has his own mission as do I.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own mission\", \"from\": 1170, \"to