\": 1897, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the straight\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not stop to talk to the media post-race, instead simply wagging a finger and laughing.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media post\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"a finger\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are ready to place the gold around his neck already at the2024 Olympicsand the athlete himself is well aware of his pre-race favourite tag.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"his neck\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"his pre-race favourite tag\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To his rivals, he said simply, \\\"If you want to win it, you have got to take it [the gold] from me.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"[the gold\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am ready.\\\"\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A gold to follow that ofKeely Hodgkinson in the 800mwould be historic making him the first British male to do so since Eric Liddell, of Chariots of Fire fame, to do so exactly 100 years ago in the same city.\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.7639463803246748, \"rank\": 0.3089923923388531, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.398414229211037e-46, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A gold\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800mwould\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"Chariots\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"Fire fame\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"the same city\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of that potential for history making, Hudson-Smith said simply: \\\"It's one step at a time.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that potential\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"history making\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"one step\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very much a person who is present right now.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to take care of the now and then I look to the future and take care of everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold would cap a remarkable journey, his career littered with injuries and following the admission when he won his first World Championship medal in 2022 that he had previously attempted to commit suicide.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable journey\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2973}, {\"ngram\": \"the admission\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"his first World Championship medal\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"suicide\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Key figures have helped to rebuild him from his coach Gary Evans to another former Olympic champion for the distance, Christine Ohuruogu, who is constantly in his ear to advise and reassure.\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\", \"score\": 0.9404359203211077, \"rank\": 0.03333333333334321, \"text\": \"Gary Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Evans_(golfer)\"}, {\"begin\": 3228, \"end\": 3246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christine Ohuruogu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Ohuruogu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Key figures\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"another former Olympic champion\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"his ear\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The combination of voices is clearly working as he has slashed half a second off his personal best already this season and, going into the final, intimates he can run quicker yet.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The combination\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"voices\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"half a second\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"the final, intimates\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know after 2021 when that reality check did hit,\\\" he said looking back on the darker days, \\\"I had a lot of talks and people basically saying to me 'it's time to take the sport seriously'.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that reality check\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"the darker days\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"talks\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3645}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I watched a podcast with Michael Johnson and he was saying that you do things not because you like it but because you have to do it.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3703, \"end\": 3718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a podcast\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no real excuses.\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no real excuses\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to avoid the gym like the plague.\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3861}, {\"ngram\": \"the plague\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a long road but I think maturity, growth and being a total overall athlete has allowed me to be the best version of myself.\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 4014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long road\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"maturity\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"growth\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3931}, {\"ngram\": \"a total overall athlete\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3965}, {\"ngram\": \"the best version\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, the results are showing.\\\"\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4107, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabet